N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 104.5 - Seed standards

State Regulations

Foundation single crosses shall be ear-inspected after
maturity by the certifying agency. They shall not contain in excess of 0.1 per
cent of definitely offtype or more than 0.2 per cent of ears with off-colored
kernels. Notes
